## Limitations

The findings are based on user-generated content, which may not always reflect expert consensus or empirical research. The perspectives gathered are subjective and may vary based on individual experiences and interpretations. Additionally, the search was limited to English-language sources, potentially excluding relevant insights from non-English speaking regions.